INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `bcatid`, `message_from`, `metadesc`, `metakeyword`, `message`, `file_path`, `slug`, `date_created`, `date_updated`) VALUES
(11, 7, 'Why does your business need custom web app development\r\n', 'If you have a website, you must know Why does your business needs custom web design and development to get more traffic. read this article to learn more.', 'Why does your business need custom web app development?, Custom Web Application Development, Custom Web App Development, Custom Website Development, ', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Why does your business need custom web app development?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/web-app-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;web application development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; attempts to give your business\r\napplication features like cross-platform and cross-browser compatibility,\r\nusability, and scalability. Each application module is built on a framework of\r\nhigh performance, security, auditability, and usability. Not only that, but\r\nwith a bespoke application, each module also takes care of the program\'s level\r\nof customization, which necessitates a thorough grasp of the organization and\r\nits particular goals and demands.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A skilled bespoke application developer understands that each organization\r\nand its requirements are distinct. As a result, they approach the task of\r\ndeveloping a bespoke application by devoting adequate time to determining the\r\nprecise business requirements and objectives.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;This enables them to offer clients some of the most cutting-edge and\r\ninventive solutions available.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A custom web app developments is usually created in three stages:\r\nconceptualization, development, and maintenance. The sort of application that\r\nis required based on your company\'s demands determines the bespoke features. As\r\na result, the bespoke apps that have been created are one-of-a-kind programmes\r\nthat have been created to suit a specific purpose. Data applications, which\r\nmight include a customer relationship management system, bespoke e-commerce\r\nsoftware, business process automation software, and so on, are the most\r\ncommonly requested forms of custom apps.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Social media integration, ERP system integration, media manipulations,\r\nand a variety of other modules are frequently required to be implemented into\r\nbespoke apps. The development process can be made more efficient by having a\r\nlibrary of these frequently used modules. A bespoke application must normally\r\nbe linked with your existing software in order to eliminate the need for\r\nnumerous entries and streamline the process. Furthermore, the custom\r\napplication is responsively designed to work on all devices.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is the procedure for creating a custom web app?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Cross-platform and cross-browser compatibility, usability, and\r\nscalability are just a few of the features that &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/web-app-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;custom web applicationdevelopment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; may provide for your business software. Each module in your app is\r\nmeticulously developed to accomplish particular duties to the highest standards\r\nof performance, safety, and security. It is only achievable, however, if the\r\ndeveloper has a thorough grasp of your company\'s objectives and requirements.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A qualified and experienced developer understands that each company\'s\r\nnature, operations, and demands are distinct. This is why, before beginning the\r\ndevelopment process, specialists spend ample time determining the specific\r\ndemands, scope, and goals of your company. They also recommend the most recent\r\ntrends, technology, and platforms, which you can use to construct an advanced\r\nand unique solution for your organization, depending on your demands and\r\nbudget.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The construction of a custom web application may be split into three\r\nfundamental steps:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: normal; margin-left: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:=&quot;&quot; &quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conceptualization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: normal; margin-left: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:=&quot;&quot; &quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Construction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: normal; margin-left: 25px;&quot;&gt;Maintenance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Your app\'s features and functionality are fully dependent on your\r\ncompany\'s requirements. Customized Customer Relationship Management software, customized\r\nE-commerce solutions, Process Automation applications, and so on are examples\r\nof custom web apps. Many of a custom web app\'s many modules are designed to\r\nimprove the system\'s performance and efficiency.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Advantages of Developing a Custom Web App&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Why is custom web application development becoming popular worldwide?\r\nThe benefits of unique software development for startups are listed below.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Let\'s take a\r\nlook at the benefits of adopting it for your company. Consider the following\r\ninstances:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.75rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;lanned to your company\'s needs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A custom web app for your company will properly fit your company\'s\r\nparticular aims and requirements. You may collaborate with a reputable web\r\napplication development company to create a web app that is perfect for your organization.\r\nIt will assist you in keeping your web app optimized for a smooth and flawless\r\noperation. Instead of including a large number of features, you may choose the\r\nmost critical ones, which will make it easier for your team to browse and\r\nenhance productivity.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Scalable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;While ready-made software may meet some of your company\'s objectives, it\r\nlacks the scalability of a unique web app.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Because custom web apps can scale with your company\'s growth, you won\'t\r\nhave to worry about choosing more expensive software or dealing with additional\r\nlicensing costs. You may add more functionality to custom web apps at any\r\nmoment without disturbing the app.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Reliable and safe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom web programmers recognize the value of data and ensure that it is\r\nsecurely protected. They save your data on distant servers that may be accessed\r\neven if your device or computer is lost or stolen. Data may be retrieved by\r\nexperts by using the cloud. To access your data, all you need is a device,\r\ninternet access, and your login credentials. It is a cost-effective option that\r\nalso saves you a significant amount of time.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom web apps are more secure than commercial web apps. Packaged\r\nsolutions are less secure since they contain various flaws that hackers are\r\naware of. Hacking a custom-coded programmed, on the other hand, is impossible.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;They\'re low-maintenance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;The best aspect about custom software is that you receive regular\r\nupdates and fantastic support around the clock, resulting in a pleasant and\r\neasy experience. Commercial software, on the other hand, lacks such\r\nfunctionality and relies on third-party programmers for updates, and support is\r\ndifficult to come by.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Boost Workplace Productivity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom web apps are capable of performing jobs efficiently, quickly, and\r\nflawlessly since they are tailored to match your individual objectives. All of\r\nyour data is well-organized and saved in one place with a bespoke app, which\r\nsaves time, effort, and enhances accuracy.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom web application methods are extremely responsive and may be used\r\nnatively on a wide range of devices to ensure a seamless flow of data.\r\nFurthermore, you can simply combine them with legacy systems to improve your\r\ncompany\'s productivity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;6.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Repetitive tasks are automated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Data travels between diverse processes and systems in a number of ways.\r\nIt may cause the system to become crowded and underperforming. Custom web apps\r\nsimplify data, ensuring that you don\'t have to manually maintain and update\r\ndata. It greatly automates different operations such as email approval, daily\r\nwork allocation, and so on, hence improving performance, increasing speed, and\r\nsaving you a lot of time. You may generate useful reports and analytics for\r\nyour company by using automated systems such as personalized CRM solutions.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;7.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Makes the most of your technological investment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;The most significant advantage of custom application development is the\r\nability to expand your current CMS without having to invest in brand new software.\r\nIt lets you get the most out of your technological investment by utilizing\r\ntools that people are already familiar with. New software necessitates\r\ntraining, which takes longer and wastes valuable time for team members.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Customized web development allows you to deploy your applications\r\non-premises or in the cloud. When you use cloud storage, you may access your\r\nfiles from anywhere and at any time.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;8.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Long-term cost-effective solution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A custom web application solution may appear pricey at first, but it\r\nwill be well worth your time and effort in the end. It provides\r\nhigher-performance and excellent outcomes since it is created with your\r\nindividual demands in mind. It automates a number of repetitive activities and\r\nimproves efficiency and accuracy, saving time and effort. Having your custom\r\nwebsite developed by a reputable company may ensure that you get significant\r\nbenefits.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;When you use commercial software, you must agree to the terms and\r\nconditions it establishes. The developers\' support is critical to your firm\'s\r\nfuture success. If the solution provider stops upgrading it, you will be forced\r\nto find a new organization in a short period of time, which will be both costly\r\nand troublesome. Custom software, on the other hand, will serve you for as long\r\nas you need it and in the manner that you need it. You may receive immediate\r\nhelp from the support team at any time of day or night.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;9.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Optimized Approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom development enables you to employ a wide range of functionality\r\nand design options, making it easier to use and search for information fast.\r\nVisitors will find it much easier to navigate the website, and they will be\r\nable to locate anything they are looking for much faster. It will assist you\r\ngreatly in a variety of ways, including lowering drop-offs and raising\r\nconversion rates.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A well-designed app has several branding and marketing advantages.\r\nFurthermore, optimization aids in the smooth operation of the custom web\r\nservice.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Words&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;By automating procedures, delivering the highest level of data\r\nprotection, and expanding with your organization, custom &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/web-app-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;web application development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; makes things a lot simpler for enterprises. If you want to\r\nestablish a custom web app for your organization, start by working with an\r\nexpert custom web app developer that can understand your goals and produce a\r\nsolid application for you.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Custom web apps provide a number of advantages to enterprises, including\r\nimproved data security and limitless updating options. An off-the-shelf product\r\nwill not fit your company\'s requirements. However, you will need to put\r\ntogether the ideal team of professionals to help you bring your concept to\r\nreality. Developers with a good background in building online and mobile\r\napplications may assist you in executing your project effectively.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;MKS Technosoft&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, as a leading web application development firm, has\r\nsubstantial expertise in building custom web application solutions for a wide\r\nrange of business demands encountered by companies across sectors. On Software Development\r\nCompany, we were named the Top &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/software-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Custom Software Development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Company. We have\r\nextensive experience with rapid tools for application development, which\r\nenables these unique apps to be constructed from the ground up in a very short\r\nperiod of time, making the entire process efficient.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#003163&quot;&gt;Tags-&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Why does your business\r\nneed custom web app development?, What is a Custom Web Application? Web app\r\ndevelopment, custom web app development, custom web app Development Company&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1648403477_custom-web-app-development.jpg', 'why-does-your-business-need-custom-web-app-development', '2022-03-27 17:51:17', '2022-06-11 11:41:02');
INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `bcatid`, `message_from`, `metadesc`, `metakeyword`, `message`, `file_path`, `slug`, `date_created`, `date_updated`) VALUES
(21, 7, 'What is a Progressive Web Application ', 'PWAs (Progressive Web Apps) is the most powerful trend in mobile web development today. PWA technology was developed by Google ', 'Progressive Web Application, PWAs, PWA Web App, Offline availability, Behavior that is similar to that of a mobile,\r\nA hassle-free installation, No submission to the app store, What are the advantages of PWA apps for desktop users', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs (Progressive Web Apps) are the most powerful\r\ntrend in mobile web development today. PWA technology was developed by Google\r\nonly a few years ago, but it quickly gained traction and is now seen as a new\r\napproach for mobile apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Learn about PWA, its primary features, and why native development should\r\nbe preferred over PWA in this post.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is a Progressive Web Application (PWA)?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/progressive-web-app-development.php&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Progressive Web Apps&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (PWAs) are web applications that use web-based\r\napplications that we\'re all familiar with, such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.\r\nThey do, however, have the look and feel of a native application. Hold on a\r\nsecond! What do we mean when we say &quot;native apps&quot;?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A native app is a software application developed in a particular\r\nprogramming language for a particular device environment, such as iOS or\r\nAndroid.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs provide features such as push notifications and the ability to\r\nfunction offline. They\'re also built on top of current APIs, making it simple\r\nto provide increased features, as well as dependability and the flexibility to\r\ninstall them on any device.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs make use of the wide range of online ecosystems, which includes\r\nmodules and communities, as well as the relative simplicity of deploying and\r\nmaintaining a website, as opposed to a native application, which is more\r\ncomplicated to construct. As a result, you can create a PWA quickly and easily.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Many firms have migrated into the product as a result of its success; we\r\nbelieve this is due to its ability to function on both &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/android-development.php&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Android&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/ios-app-development.php&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;iOS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; without\r\nmuch change. Twitter, Pinterest, Uber, Tiktok, Spotify, Jumia (Africa\'s biggest\r\ne-commerce site), and others are just a few instances of notable firms that\r\nhave PWAs for their goods.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The fact that such items can all be installed on your home screen, that\r\nthey can continue to function offline from where you last left them, and that\r\nthey provide a basis for comparison and features to their native applications\r\nare all common characteristics.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs are similar to native mobile apps in that they have certain\r\nexpectations that must be satisfied in order to provide a successful product\r\nfor user use. Let\'s take a look at what makes an excellent PWA.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The following are some of the most important\r\nadvantages of PWA apps:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Offline availability&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;If your internet connection is slow or non-existent, your website will\r\nnot show the material properly. Mobile applications, on the other hand,\r\nfrequently identify and allow users to utilize them even when they are not\r\nconnected to the internet. As a result, they are more accessible and encourage\r\nparticipation. PWA also provides this service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Behavior that is similar to that of a mobile&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/progressive-web-app-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Progressive Web Applications&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; are similar to mobile apps, but they\r\ninclude website features such as dynamic data and database access. Most PWAs\r\ntake advantage of existing technologies and UX/UI that enable them to provide\r\nbetter user experiences than traditional websites. PWAs, on the other hand,\r\nfunction similarly to websites and are search engine indexable, which helps to\r\nincrease their visibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. A hassle-free installation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Users may download a PWA from a website and install it immediately on\r\ntheir device. A PWA, like a mobile app, has its own icon on phones and tablets.\r\nAdditionally, you may submit your software to the Google Play Store for more\r\ninteraction (the Apple App Store currently does not allow this).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. No submission to the app store.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You don\'t have to put your PWA in the app store. As a natural result,\r\ncompanies are given the time and effort to submit their apps to app stores.\r\nAlso, teams may send new updates to users without having to wait for approval;\r\nthe changes are downloaded and updated instantly when users reopen the app.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;5. Take advantage of hardware characteristics.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Different mobile functionalities, such as push notifications, can be\r\nincluded. The best part is that developers have complete control over their\r\ndevelopment, which might open up new marketing and sales channels for firms.\r\nAdditionally, PWAs may take advantage of mobile device hardware capabilities\r\nlike geolocation and cameras.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What are the advantages of PWA apps for desktop users?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Progressive Web Programs (PWPs), like native apps, may be installed on\r\ndesktop devices. PWAs have the capability to provide lots of new advantages to\r\ndesktop users. They\'re lighter than native desktop apps, for example. They update\r\nautomatically in the background, so there\'s no need to push consumers to update\r\ntheir applications manually. PWAs are simple to set up and are dependable.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs are being adopted by a growing number of businesses and\r\ngovernmental organizations, not only because they are affordable to construct\r\nbut also because they provide increased interaction.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Let\'s have a look at a brief rundown of the advantages\r\nof a PWA:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The updates are self-contained; you do not need to go to the Play Store to get them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They\'re made using standard web tools.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They\'re both quick and light.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Unlike other websites, they function offline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They may be found via a search engine.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They are simple to set up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Low-cost maintenance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Future of Progressive Web Apps&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;According to Gartner, PWAs are expected to replace 50% of mobile\r\napplications by 2020. PWA is a rapidly growing technology that many analysts\r\nfeel will be the future of mobile development.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Many data-driven enterprise apps that don\'t require native development\r\nand deployment will very certainly be produced as PWAs. Business-to-employee\r\napplications are an example of this. If native applications are great PWA\r\nprospects, there\'s no reason to spend a lot of effort and money developing\r\nthem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Users, on the other hand, don\'t download and maintain as many apps on\r\ntheir smartphones as they formerly did. That\'s why companies will explore methods\r\nto reduce the barrier to entry and the expense of mobile development &ndash; and\r\nthat\'s when they\'ll turn to the PWA.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;When should you use native applications instead of PWA\r\napps?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Even though PWAs have a lot of advantages, native applications are\r\nfrequently a superior option. If you want to use a native app, you should:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You need to provide your users with the best experience possible (faster and smoother animations),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Your app must be able to communicate with other native apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Your app should have more functionality than a PWA (for example, geofencing),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You wish to alter and improve the user interface.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Advanced features are required for your app (for example, social networking).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They work in the same way as traditional native apps do.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They are responsive and adapt to a variety of screen sizes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;What Are the Differences Between Native and PWA Apps?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Cost of Development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs are less expensive to create than native apps.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;When creating a native app, you\'ll need to learn a programming language\r\nand then create separate versions of the app for Android and iOS devices. On\r\nthe other hand, you may hire an experienced expert to complete the task for\r\nyou, which will be more expensive.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You\'ll need resources in the future to maintain and update the software,\r\nwhich will cost a lot of money and effort.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In the case of a PWA, you can have a single codebase for all platforms.\r\nIt also saves time since you won\'t have to build it from scratch; instead, you\r\nmay adapt your present website to meet the requirements.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;And, unlike native, where you may employ up to two developers depending\r\non where you require your app, if you hire a developer, you will only be able\r\nto hire one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Discoverability&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Native applications aren\'t indexed by search engines, so you\'ll have to\r\ngo to the App/Play store\'s website to find them. Software Store Optimization\r\n(ASO) can help you make your app more searchable in the App or Play store, but\r\nthat\'s a different subject.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;PWAs, unlike native applications, function similarly to webpages,\r\nallowing them to be indexed by search engines. This improves their search\r\nengine rankings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Safety&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In today\'s world, a website must be encrypted with an SSL certificate in\r\norder to function, which provides an extra degree of protection. PWAs, as we\r\nall know, are websites that have been transformed into apps, making them more\r\nsecure since they operate over HTTPS. These really are safety protocols that\r\nenable the secure flow of data between the client and the server, preventing\r\ntampering.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You must use various security techniques, like multi-factor\r\nauthentication, to safeguard your native apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Do you need PWA developers for your next project? &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/contactus.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Get in&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/contactus.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;touch with us&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;; we know how to create apps that leverage this technology to\r\npropel your company forward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;line-height: 32px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-family: &quot; open=&quot;&quot; sans&quot;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 26px;&quot;=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;#085294&quot;&gt;Tags-&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#424242&quot; face=&quot;Open Sans, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 26px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;What is a Progressive Web Application,&amp;nbsp;Progressive Web Application, PWAs, PWA Web App, Offline availability, Behavior that is similar to that of a mobile,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;', 'uploads/1649696378_what-is-a-progressive-web-app.jpg', 'what-is-a-progressive-web-application', '2022-04-10 17:48:00', '2022-06-01 09:00:28');
INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `bcatid`, `message_from`, `metadesc`, `metakeyword`, `message`, `file_path`, `slug`, `date_created`, `date_updated`) VALUES
(23, 11, 'What is the significance of website design and development', 'What is the significance of website design and development, and how does it contribute to the profitability of your company?', 'Website Design, Website Development, Static Website, Dynamic Website Development, CMS Website Development, Responsive Website Design', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;What is the significance of website\r\ndesign and development, and how does it contribute to the profitability of your\r\ncompany?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;With the introduction of new technology, it\r\nis all too easy to miss valuable opportunities. This scenario gets worse\r\nwhen one lacks the expertise to recognize these shifts. This is the case for\r\ncompanies with little knowledge of website creation and design.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Website development agencies have\r\nrevolutionized the way businesses are run. So, if&nbsp;businesses want to know\r\nthe value of websites, this post will be for them.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The following are the most important\r\nadvantages of website development and web design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Makes it simple to navigate&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;A successful online marketplace allows users\r\nto navigate easily. Essentially, the material on the website should be easily\r\naccessible. As a result, the pages should load quickly.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;As a result, the website, such as an online\r\nauto parts store, must provide options to help with navigating. This includes\r\nthe presence of a search box. Users can use the search function to easily find\r\nthe area they want. A developer&nbsp;achieves it through an&nbsp;excellent web\r\ndesign.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Aside from creating the website, the developer\r\nshould test the pages for navigational ease on a regular basis. This is done to\r\neliminate or fix problems that may make it difficult to load web pages.\r\nRemember that a website with effective navigation is guaranteed to receive more\r\norganic traffic.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Use SEO to your advantage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Whenever it comes to websites, Search Engine\r\nOptimization SEO has become an important factor to consider. With millions of\r\nwebsites viewing for the top spot in &lt;b&gt;search engine results pages (SERPs)&lt;/b&gt;,\r\nsearch engines had to come up with a strategy to organize websites.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Well, one can achieve a higher position by\r\nusing site development and design. Title tags, keyword usage, image\r\noptimization, and linking are all factors to consider. This indicates that the\r\nwebsite meets all of the criteria for being ranked first.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Second, optimization makes your website\r\nmore user-friendly. Apart from websites, webmasters can retain long-awaited\r\nusers. Under this,&nbsp; &lt;span class=&quot;MsoHyperlink&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/website-development.php&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;website development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\nis obliged to include features such as &quot;Call to Action&quot;. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;This\r\nalso needs to simplify the design of the page. Next, learn more about the\r\nexpected load speeds. With this optimization, your website will be displayed in\r\nvarious queries. In this way, the website gets more clicks in the search\r\nresults.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Provide visual content on the website &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Truth be told, selling abstract products and\r\nservices can be tedious. It gets even more complicated when a company only\r\nprovides tons of text on its major. This is where website development spice\r\nthings up.&nbsp; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;By\r\ncontacting a professional web designer, business owners can decide which images\r\nto use. Furthermore, the company has the freedom to choose the number of\r\npromotional videos and images. This will be guided by &lt;span class=&quot;MsoHyperlink&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/seo-company-india.php&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;SEO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;The\r\nadvantage of using visual content is that it gives the user a clear picture of\r\nwhat the product looks like. Obviously, not all customers understand the\r\nservices or products offered by SMS. Therefore, the inclusion of images\r\nfacilitates the transmission of the message. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Further, the website\'s usage of graphics\r\neasily attracts users\' interest. Before browsing text, users are often\r\ninterested in images. This improves the chances of having more users on the\r\nsite. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;However, webmasters should avoid cramming with\r\nvisual data. Indeed, this makes it difficult for users to interpret. It also\r\nreduces website rankings from search engine optimization. Therefore, it is\r\nimportant to moderate the use of images.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Increase the sales &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;The\r\namount of sales made has an impact on a company\'s performance. Creating a\r\nwebsite, on the other hand, can help a company attract more customers.\r\nEcommerce operations are expected to expand by 21.3 percent by 2019, according\r\nto Statista (a Germany-based statistical company). This suggests that online purchases\r\nare attracting more visitors.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;These days, many business owners are ready\r\nto do their transactions online. This is because they saw a great opportunity\r\nto take advantage of online sales. The increase in sales is closely related to\r\nthe increase in the number of customers. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Webmasters are encouraged to include updates\r\nto further promote sales. Updates and upgrades will make your site more\r\nfunctional. In addition, show customers that the brand is committed to\r\nproviding exemplary service and information. &nbsp;Another way to increase sales is to insert\r\npromotions. This is where you can generate the fuzz you really need among your\r\nusers. This leads to more sales. It also gives users the impression that they\r\ncan buy affordable products from the company. Therefore, every activity on the\r\nwebsite adds value to the company in some way.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Attract lifetime customers to your\r\nbusiness &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Having loyal customers is paramount, as the\r\ncompany strives to expand and expand its wings. However, this can be a daunting\r\ntask. Especially when entrepreneurs use bad tactics to achieve it. At this\r\npoint, website development and design can help. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Metrics retrieved from the website allow\r\nwebmasters to monitor user activity. Here you can emphasize the customers who\r\ncontinue to support your brand. After identifying them, business owners need to\r\nfind creative ways to retain these customers. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;An\r\ninnovative way is to reward them with gift certificates and perks. This will\r\ndefinitely give them more reasons to access your service or product. Through\r\nthe website, business owners should remember to make sure that loyal customers\r\nare not left behind. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Another attraction for lifetime users is the\r\nability to market the brand. So you work indirectly for the company. This also\r\nreduces marketing costs.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Reach out to extra customers&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;One of the principal desires of setting up\r\na corporation is to develop in phrases of the consumer base. Well, there\'s a\r\nmyriad of approaches to acquire this however everyone has extraordinary results.\r\nWhen it involves internet improvement and design, there are a few essential\r\nmilestones achieved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;The first one is that it places the logo\r\ncall out there. Essentially, whilst the internet site is to be had on Worldwide\r\nWeb then the organization is on an international platform. This way that the\r\nlittle-recognized corporation may be searched and offer merchandise to distant\r\nclients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;These are the services that are designed to\r\nmake it easier for clients to get directly into the activities. Here, there are\r\ndifferent alternatives along with buying or ordering the product at the\r\ninternet site. Furthermore, the organization nevertheless continues in contact\r\nwith the neighborhood clients. Great right!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Improving person engagement&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Traditionally, an organization was housed\r\nin a physical structure. However, as more services have gone digital, the\r\nsituation has changed. As a result, marketers are encouraged to promote\r\nhigh-quality websites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;In this platform, it\'s miles pretty clean\r\nto hold an excellent rapport with the cease person. This includes retrieving\r\nremarks on the products and services offered. So you may have interaction with\r\nthem and offer important responses to the queries asked. Additionally, there\'s\r\nno difficulty at the time of activity. By automating the offerings at the\r\ninternet site, customers are assured of spherical the clock offerings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Also below person engagement, the weblog or\r\nweb website online proprietor can preserve clients published in any respect\r\ninstances. For instance, if new rate prices are brought then clients are a\r\nnumber of the first to know.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Familiar with marketing and advertising &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;If a start-up needs to succeed, it is\r\nessential to bring products and services to market. However, marketing\r\nstrategies can help you sell your brand. Website design and development are\r\npocket-friendly compared to tactics such as using main media and billboards. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Companies can use this online platform to view\r\nall relevant information. This includes Products/services offered, location,\r\nprice, reputation, contact information, etc. Webmasters can conveniently place\r\nattractive offers on their websites. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Interestingly, it\'s easier to update the site\'s amazing discounts and\r\noffers. Therefore, there is no downtime waiting for your ad to run. The same