ere, webmasters can make fun of their readers with a new look even before launch. Overall, these changes can be implemented consistently.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;How Website Designing and Development\r\ncan make a Company&rsquo;s Profit making?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;1. Cost reduction &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Unfortunately, many start-ups and large\r\ncompanies are failing to plan because of their low profits. This is despite the\r\nhigh expectations for the investment made. The main failures of any business are\r\ndue to the use of inadequate business tactics, such as web service negligence. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;You\r\nneed to know that website design and development are affordable. By properly\r\norganizing your content, webmasters can save a lot of web development costs.\r\nThe cost-cutting aspect extends to the future benefits that websites bring to\r\nyour business. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;In\r\naddition, this website reduces the distance traveled to reach customers. Physically\r\ntalking to potential customers consumes a lot of resources. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Web services come in handy in this\r\nsituation. Moreover, reducing such additional costs means that the company will\r\nmake more profits. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;2. Allow advertising on the site &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Business owners must have come across many ads\r\nthat are shown on various websites. This is one of the most attractive ways for\r\nbusinesses to increase their&nbsp;profits. Other businesses have asked the\r\ncompany to place advertisements on its website.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;As\r\npart of marketing and advertising, the host\'s website charges a certain amount\r\nto serve the ad. Second, it\'s important to create a unique and reputable\r\nwebsite. By focusing on this, webmasters can put the spotlight on their\r\nwebsites. The big winner here is that the site attracts more business and\r\nadvertising. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;3. E-commerce &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;As\r\nmentioned earlier, products and services have moved from stores to online\r\nplatforms. One of the most important online venues is the website. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Take\r\nAmazon, which accounts for 44% of total US e-commerce sales. In addition,\r\nStatista (Germany base statistical company) emphasized that the company was\r\nable to earn $ 108.35 million in 2017.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Conclusion &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;After a thorough and detailed explanation of\r\nthe importance of a website, several aspects become apparent. Firstly,\r\ncompanies need to strive to develop and design customized websites. Secondly,\r\nit\'s important to put your best foot forward. Therefore, a website or blog is\r\nconsidered to meet and exceed the guidelines. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;But\r\nit\'s up to the webmaster to take that big step and develop the website.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;If you are looking for website design and\r\ndevelopment you can consult &lt;span class=&quot;MsoHyperlink&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;MKS Technosoft&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; company.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1652537690_what-is-the-significance-of-website-design.jpg', 'what-is-the-significance-of-website-design-and-development', '2022-05-14 14:14:50', '2022-05-23 12:38:36'),
(24, 11, 'Importance of Website Maintenance', 'It is necessary that the information on your website be updated on a regular basis. website maintenance increases your website security.', 'website maintenance services, website maintenance services near me, best website maintenance company, mobile app maintenance', '&lt;p&gt;Website Maintenance: Website maintenance is the process of regularly monitoring website errors and ensuring that everything is fully updated and responsive.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Everyone knows how important a well-structured website is. But simply launching and running your site is not enough. Owning a website is like owning a home or car-it requires regular attention and maintenance. Depending on the size of your business, your website may require monthly, weekly, or daily maintenance. Maintaining your website properly can help you improve the number of new visitors, boost return traffic, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We\'d like to explain some of the primary reasons why we believe it\'s critical to keep your site up to date. Your company may be falling behind the competition if you don\'t have a website maintenance and support plan in place.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What does the Website Maintenance Services List include?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;We\'ve already covered the basics\r\nof what website upkeep entails. It\'s now time to go over the key services that\r\nare included in the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/website-maintenance.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Website Maintenance Services&lt;/a&gt; List.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. It &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improves\r\n     Security&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The primary reason for website\r\nupkeep is security. If your organization is using a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/cms-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Content Management System&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n(CMS) such as Drupal or WordPress, you will want to ensure that your site is\r\nkeeping up with software patches and security updates. Otherwise, hackers have\r\nthe opportunity to steal data from your website.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. It\r\n     increases website traffic&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;To provide searchers with the\r\nhighest quality content, search engines like Google raise the ranking of\r\nregularly updated websites. The higher the ranking, the more visible your site\r\nis and the more likely your content will be displayed when your audience\r\nsearches for relevant keywords. Update your website with valuable information,\r\nfix broken links, remove duplicate pages, keep your content up-to-date, and\r\nattract both new visitors and repeaters.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. It\r\n     optimises the visitor\'s experience&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;By regularly updating your\r\nwebsite with shareable content such as upcoming events, image galleries, and\r\nblogs, your viewers will know who you are and what you are doing. A\r\nwell-maintained website will help you promote your brand, your job, and your\r\nmission. Remove outdated information and perform website audits to track\r\nwebsite issues and errors. Do this frequently to ensure that your visitors have\r\nthe best possible user experience. Website maintenance is important for all &lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;either &lt;/span&gt;large\r\nor small. Regular maintenance of your website improves performance and provides\r\na secure environment for your visitors.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;4&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. Web\r\n     maintenance &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue-underline&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Enable scheduled backup&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;4&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Backups may be required\r\nregardless of whether they are needed for recovery or development purposes.\r\nEven with standard backup solutions, there is a risk that the server will be\r\nhacked and unwanted users will access your website\'s data.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;5&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;5. Taking\r\n     care of your website can improve SEO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;5&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Do you know your &lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;website&lt;/span&gt; ranking on Google for your target keywords?\r\nMost website owners don\'t! Professional website maintenance helps you stay\r\nahead of the competition by tracking and improving SEO.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;6. Website\r\n     maintenance can enhance your brand\'s reputation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;How do customers see if your\r\nbrand website is slow or broken? In most cases, it is unstable, unprofessional,\r\nand weak. As a result, you will have less business. Even a minute of\r\ninterruption can result in an extraordinary loss of profit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;=&quot;&quot; mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;7&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;7. Remove\r\n     spam comments.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;7&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Security would be the main reason\r\nfor &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/website-maintenance.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Website Maintenance&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;. Look for\r\nspam that may have passed the filter. Regular vulnerability scans prevent your\r\nwebsite from being attacked or hijacked.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;8&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;8. Fixes\r\n     and repairs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;8&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;This is all related to 404\r\nerrors, bugs, and broken links. Both internal and external links must be\r\nchecked. You can run the link checker to find broken links that frustrate users\r\nand lower their search engine rankings.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;9&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;9. Browser\r\n     compatibility test&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;9&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Make sure that all aspects of\r\nyour website work correctly in the most popular browsers. Your website should\r\nalso be compatible with lesser-used browsers.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;10&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;10. Software\r\n     update&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;10&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;You need to update important\r\nsoftware that your website depends on. For example&amp;nbsp;content management systems&lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;their themes, and\r\nplugins. Also, if it\'s worth using, update non-essential software.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;11&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;11. Website\r\n     content&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;11&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The fresh and updated content of\r\nyour website is something that users and search engines love. Therefore, check\r\nthe content regularly, correct any mistakes, and upload new information in a\r\nfresh style, including target words.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;These are the basics of website\r\nmaintenance services. Companies can dig deeper into it through their websites,\r\nbut don\'t ignore it. Maintaining a website is an easy way to succeed online in\r\nyour business. Maintenance actually guarantees the highest level of website\r\nperformance by eliminating bugs and security issues and providing the best user\r\nexperience for your customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Website maintenance plans can\r\nprovide 24/7 website uptime, security, and performance monitoring to avoid\r\nthese issues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;There are\r\nlists of website maintenance tasks that need to be performed on a regular\r\nbasis:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conducted\r\nweekly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure all the pages load correctly.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Back up and make sure you have saved the previous version of the website.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Update the website software and plugins.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure all forms are running correctly.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Remove all spam comments from pages and posts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Look for any broken links on the page.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Find and fix 404 errors or redirect&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create blog posts to keep your community interested and drive SEO traffic.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Conducted every month&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check the loading speed of the website and make sure it is not slowing down.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check the security scan to make sure nothing is wrong.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Examine the previous month\'s website statistics&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check your blog for any newly updated articles.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&quot;;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Implemented quarterly&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Review your website design and structure&mdash;can it be improved?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Should anything be updated in terms of graphics and images?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check your SEO, Meta titles, and descriptions to make sure they\'re as effective as possible.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Test and improve popups, forms, and action buttons&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check the efficiency of your workload to see if there is anything you can automate.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check that your website works properly on all devices and browsers.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check your ads and marketing campaigns to see if they need to be changed or updated.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check the backup status and restore the previous version of the website.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;red-underline&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Conducted &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-IN&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;every\r\nyear&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;All references to the current year should be updated.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check each page for content accuracy, grammar, typos, and relevance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check all active email addresses to see if they are redundant and can be deleted&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure the website domain name is updated.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Consider whether a website design update is planned&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check all high-performance blog posts to see if they can be updated with new content&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;To sum up,&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Websites are never complete.\r\nThroughout the year, a lot of things happen on your website that needs to be\r\nevaluated on a regular basis. You are probably investing a lot of money in your\r\nwebsite. Therefore, you need to maintain this investment. There\'s a lot you\r\nneed to get the most out of your website, from content to viruses to outdated\r\nlinks. It\'s critical to have a good website maintenance plan unless you have\r\nyour own IT department with expert programmers and webmasters. Simply put,\r\nwebsite maintenance, like car and home maintenance, is essential to keeping\r\nthings safe and functioning. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;blue-complex-underline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;=&quot;&quot; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;=&quot;&quot; mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The benefits of investing in a website maintenance plan\r\nfrequently outweigh the price because website errors harm both your reputation\r\nand your profit margin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;MKS Technosoft&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; assists you with\r\nthe maintenance and support needs of all your websites. Contact our helpful\r\nteam immediately, and we\'ll assist you in maximizing the potential of your\r\nwebsite and business. Click here for help and advice on website maintenance and support with a leading website Development\r\nCompany in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;root-block-node&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; calibri&quot;,sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:=&quot;&quot; minor-latin;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#085294&quot;&gt;Tags-&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Importance of Website Maintenance, W&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; open=&quot;&quot; sans&quot;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 18px;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;ebsite Maintenance Services, Website Maintenance Services near me, Best Website Maintenance Company, Mobile app Maintenance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; open=&quot;&quot; sans&quot;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 18px;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;', 'uploads/1653574121_website-maintenance.png', 'importance-of-website-maintenance', '2022-05-26 14:08:41', '2022-05-26 15:46:29');
INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `bcatid`, `message_from`, `metadesc`, `metakeyword`, `message`, `file_path`, `slug`, `date_created`, `date_updated`) VALUES
(25, 11, 'Difference Between Static and Dynamic Websites', 'The significant difference between static and dynamic websites is that the material on a static website remains constant, whereas information on a dynamic website changes frequently.', 'Difference Between Static and Dynamic Websites, Static and dynamic websites, Static Website, Dynamic Websites', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&quot;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif;=&quot;&quot; background-image:=&quot;&quot; initial;=&quot;&quot; background-position:=&quot;&quot; background-size:=&quot;&quot; background-repeat:=&quot;&quot; background-attachment:=&quot;&quot; background-origin:=&quot;&quot; background-clip:=&quot;&quot; initial;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;There are several\r\nvariables to consider while creating a company website. Many company owners are\r\nperplexed when it comes to choosing between a static and dynamic website. They\r\nboth have their own set of benefits, drawbacks, and capabilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Static websites simply said, are pre-built and capable of\r\nshowing the same content to all viewers. These web pages are frequently created\r\nusing HTML. A dynamic website, on the other hand, is more sophisticated since\r\nit may show different content to people using different devices or based on\r\ntheir demographics. Browsing dynamic websites become more interesting and\r\npleasurable as a result of this.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;It speaks to the fact that static websites take less time to\r\ncreate than dynamic websites.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Before we get into the comparison, it\'s vital to understand\r\nhow the internet as a whole delivers visitors to your website. The internet, in\r\nsimple words, is made up of a server that keeps all website files and a browser\r\nthat allows users to view them. To create a connection between a server and a\r\nbrowser, several connections must exist. There are two types of connections,\r\neither of which you\'ve undoubtedly encountered. The first is HTTP (Hypertext\r\nTransfer Protocol), whereas the second is HTTPS (Hypertext Transfer Protocol\r\nSecure).&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;On that topic, let us examine both of these sorts of\r\nwebsites and how they vary. Begin with the static webpage.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;In this article, we will know about Static and Dynamic\r\nWebsites.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;There are several variables to consider while creating a\r\ncompany website. Many company owners are perplexed when it comes to choosing\r\n&lt;b&gt;between a static and dynamic website.&lt;/b&gt; They both have their own set of benefits,\r\ndrawbacks, and capabilities.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Static websites simply said, are pre-built and capable of\r\nshowing the same content to all viewers. These web pages are frequently created\r\nusing HTML. A dynamic website, on the other hand, is more sophisticated since\r\nit may show different content to people using different devices or based on\r\ntheir demographics. Browsing dynamic websites become more interesting and\r\npleasurable as a result of this.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;It speaks to the fact that static websites take less time to\r\ncreate than dynamic websites.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Before we get into the comparison, it\'s vital to understand\r\nhow the internet as a whole delivers visitors to your website. The internet, in\r\nsimple words, is made up of a server that keeps all website files and a browser\r\nthat allows users to view them. To create a connection between a server and a\r\nbrowser, several connections must exist. There are two types of connections,\r\neither of which you\'ve undoubtedly encountered. The first is HTTP (Hypertext\r\nTransfer Protocol), whereas the second is HTTPS (Hypertext Transfer Protocol\r\nSecure).&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;On that topic, let us examine both of these sorts of\r\nwebsites and how they vary. Begin with the static webpage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is a dynamic website, exactly?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Static websites focus on information rather than interactive\r\ncomponents.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;(*Interactive components: An interactive element is\r\nsomething where the user may interact or everything that can be clicked)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#085294&quot;&gt;Also Read&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;MsoHyperlink&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/bolg.php/importance-of-website-maintenance&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Importance\r\nof Website Maintenance&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;On the other side, dynamic fluid-design websites contain\r\nmore interactive aspects that contribute to the overall user experience. Users\r\nwill be able to interact with the elements on the page more readily, increasing\r\ntotal page retention time, which is good for &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/seo-company-india.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Search Engine Optimization&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. These dynamic websites need\r\nthe use of a lot of HTML code.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The static website, on the other hand, solely uses\r\nclient-side HTML and CSS code. Dynamic websites must respond to user requests\r\non both the client-side and the server-side.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;To create the interactive portions of the website that will\r\nrespond to user queries, developers must employ server-side scripting languages\r\nsuch as ASP, JavaScript, PHP, and others. Developers must utilize server-side\r\nscripting languages such as ASP, JavaScript, PHP, and others to create\r\ninteractive elements of the website that respond to user queries. When a user\r\nviews any area of a dynamic website, the code may be altered and the site can\r\nrespond to the input. It might have been obtaining data, playing movies, or\r\nrequesting files from the server.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;In-depth exploration of the significance&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Static referred to something that is fixed and does not\r\nchange if the input is given by a human. Furthermore, when a user interacts\r\nwith or views a website element, no changes are made. These are the primary\r\npages, which largely include text-based content.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;A dynamic website, on the other hand, is one whose elements\r\nare continually changing in response to user requests. Dynamic websites can\r\ninclude personalization, interaction, and functionality. One thing to bear in\r\nmind is that there are several technologies available for developing a dynamic\r\nwebsite.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Let us pause for a moment to discuss specifics.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Before deciding which kind to utilize, it is vital to\r\nunderstand how websites are created. Static websites are created using HTML and\r\nCSS and do not require any extra tools to develop or maintain. Dynamic\r\nwebsites, on the other hand, require both client-side and server-side support\r\nto perform successfully. On these websites, HTML is utilized to govern the\r\ninteractive front-end components, while server-side languages are used to\r\nmanage the response elements.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;You may employ a range of characteristics and capabilities\r\nto make a dynamic website more seamless and user-friendly. Keep in mind that\r\ndynamic websites use more server resources and may take longer to load. A\r\nfaster server is required to load the page quickly. However, even if the server\r\nis not cloud-based, the static website loads significantly quicker.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Coding differences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Even if you are new to coding and studying the fundamentals\r\nof HTML and CSS, you should be able to understand how a static website is\r\nconstructed. Greater degrees of experience, abilities, and subject knowledge are\r\nstill necessary to produce the best results. There are several ways available\r\nto guide you through the process of designing these websites.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;When it comes to dynamic websites, however, there are\r\nseveral factors to consider and keep in mind. You may need to use sophisticated\r\nJS like React, to make it more responsive, unique-looking, and faster. When it\r\ncomes to coding, the options for personalization and functionality on dynamic\r\nwebsites are limitless.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Which one should I choose?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;So the important question here is which websites you should\r\nselect and which websites are appropriate for your business. The solution is\r\nobvious. A static website is a fantastic alternative if you conduct enough\r\nbusiness to display static content while still generating business leads.\r\nDynamic websites, on the other hand, make more sense if you\'re in an industry\r\nlike &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/ecommerce-development.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;e-commerce&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; or a startup environment where you need to attract people by\r\nnarrative.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;When it comes to website development, static websites are\r\nless expensive than dynamic ones. This is because developers must customize\r\neach piece to get the intended engagement. Conduct preliminary market research\r\nto establish the sort of website required to attract the bulk of your business\r\nleads. Having a website is critical to being relevant in this very competitive\r\nfield. So, if you don\'t already have a website, get one to improve your\r\ninternet reputation and brand equity.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;What are the most significant differences between static\r\nand dynamic websites?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The major &lt;b&gt;difference between a static and dynamic website &lt;/b&gt;is\r\nthat the content of a static website remains unchanged unless the source code\r\nis changed by the website developer. Information on dynamic websites may change\r\ndepending on the needs of the user, their location, and the time of day.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;A web page is typically used to upload static content.\r\nRegardless of the action taken, anything the user sees is downloaded and\r\ndisplayed in the same way. The content format of dynamic websites varies\r\ndepending on the controls and user behavior that the website administrator\r\nspecifies.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;A static website brings it simpler to obtain information.\r\nIt\'s possible that doing so with a dynamic website will be more challenging&lt;b&gt;.&lt;/b&gt;\r\nStatic material can be stored or cached on a content delivery network (CDN)\r\nedge server for faster access to information. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Caching the content of a web page speeds up the loading of a\r\nuser\'s website. This is due to the international distribution of Edge servers.\r\nAs a result, CDNs provide faster and more reliable responses to nearby users.\r\nHowever, the material of dynamic sites changes regularly, so it\'s not practical\r\nto do the same. Caching personal data introduces new security\r\nvulnerabilities.&nbsp; Another important\r\ndifference between static and dynamic websites is that the content of the\r\nstatic website is retrieved directly from the server, not elsewhere. Before the\r\ndynamic material is downloaded from the server, it needs to go through several\r\nlayers of application logic.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;If you have still doubt about the&nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Differences&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;Between\r\nStatic and Dynamic Websites &lt;/b&gt;feel free to contact a&lt;b&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;reputed &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/website-development-in-patna.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Website Development in Patna&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Our team will help and guide you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=&quot;&quot; &quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;color:#085294;mso-fareast-language:en-us&quot;=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#003163&quot;&gt;Tags-&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 19.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=&quot;&quot; &quot;times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;color:#424242;mso-fareast-language:en-us&quot;=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt;&quot;&gt;Difference between\r\nStatic and Dynamic Websites, Static and dynamic websites, Static Website,\r\nDynamic Websites&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1654182964_static-vs-dynamic-website.png', 'difference-between-static-and-dynamic-websites', '2022-06-02 15:16:04', '2022-12-01 14:03:03'),
(26, 11, 'Benefits of a website redesign.', 'One of the main benefits of redesigning a website is improving the user experience. A well-designed website can make it easy for users.', 'Benefits of a website redesign.', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:=&quot;&quot; calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;mso-ansi-language:en-in;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Benefits of Website\r\nRedesign.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Redesigning\r\na website can have numerous benefits for both the website owner and its users.\r\nIn this article, we will discuss why redesigning a website can be beneficial\r\nand how it can help improve the overall user experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improving user experience&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;One\r\nof the main benefits of redesigning a website is improving the user experience.\r\nA well-designed website can make it easy for users to find what they are\r\nlooking for, navigate the website and complete tasks such as making a purchase\r\nor filling out a form. By improving the user experience, businesses can\r\nincrease customer satisfaction and reduce bounce rates.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; color:#252525;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;A redesign can help address these issues by focusing on UX improvements\r\nsuch as:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Simplifying the\r\n     navigation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n     A website with too many menus, dropdowns, and links can be overwhelming\r\n     for users. A redesign can simplify the navigation and make it easier for\r\n     users to find what they are looking for.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Improving load\r\n     times:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n     Slow load times can be a major frustration for users. A website redesign\r\n     can optimize the website\'s code and reduce page load times.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Enhancing mobile\r\n     responsiveness:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n     More and more people are accessing websites on their mobile devices, so\r\n     it\'s essential that websites are optimized for mobile. A redesign can\r\n     ensure that the website looks and functions well on mobile devices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Enhancing mobile responsiveness&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;With\r\nthe rise of mobile devices, it is more important than ever for websites to be\r\nmobile-friendly. A website that is not mobile-responsive can be difficult to\r\nnavigate on a smaller screen, which can lead to a frustrating user experience.\r\nRedesigning a website can ensure that it is optimized for all devices,\r\nincluding desktops, laptops, tablets, and smartphones.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improving Search Engine Optimization (SEO)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A\r\nwell-designed website can also help improve search engine optimization (SEO).\r\nBy redesigning a website, businesses can optimize it for keywords and improve\r\nits page speed, both of which can help improve search engine rankings. This, in\r\nturn, can lead to increased organic traffic and more potential customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;Another major\r\n     benefit of redesigning a website is the potential to improve search engine\r\n     visibility. Search engine optimization (SEO) is the process of optimizing\r\n     a website so that it ranks higher in search engine results pages (SERPs).\r\n     A well-designed website that is optimized for SEO can help drive more\r\n     traffic to the site.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; color:#252525;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:=&quot;&quot; ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;A redesign can help to improve SEO in a number of ways:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:=&quot;&quot; calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;mso-ansi-language:en-in;=&quot;&quot; mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ensuring that the website is\r\n     mobile-friendly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;:\r\n     As mentioned earlier, mobile responsiveness is critical for SEO. Google\r\n     has stated that it considers mobile-friendliness as a ranking factor, so a\r\n     mobile-friendly website is essential.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Improving site speed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;: site speed is\r\n     another ranking factor that can impact SEO. A website redesign can\r\n     optimize the website\'s code and reduce page load times, improving the\r\n     site\'s speed.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ensuring that the website is accessible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;: Accessibility\r\n     is also a ranking factor that can impact SEO. A redesign can ensure that\r\n     the website is accessible to users with disabilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Updating Design Trends&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Design\r\ntrends are constantly changing, and a website that looks outdated can make a\r\nbusiness appear unprofessional. Redesigning a website can help businesses stay\r\nup-to-date with the latest design trends and ensure that their website looks\r\nmodern and fresh.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Increasing Conversion Rates&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Redesigning\r\na website can also help increase conversion rates. A well-designed website that\r\nis easy to navigate and optimized for conversions can encourage users to take\r\naction, such as making a purchase or filling out a form. This can lead to\r\nincreased revenue and a higher return on investment (ROI) for businesses.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;A conversion\r\n     occurs when a user takes a desired action on a website, such as making a\r\n     purchase or filling out a contact form. Redesigning a website can help\r\n     improve conversion rates by making it easier for users to take these\r\n     desired actions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;A\r\nredesign can improve conversion rates in a number of ways:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Simplifying the checkout process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;: If the website\r\n     has an e-commerce component, simplifying the checkout process can help\r\n     reduce cart abandonment rates and improve conversion rates.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Optimizing forms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;: If the website\r\n     has forms, optimizing them can help increase conversion rates. This could\r\n     involve simplifying the form, reducing the number of required fields, or\r\n     making the form more visually appealing.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Adding calls to action (CTAs)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=&quot;&quot; en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;: CTAs are\r\n     buttons or links that encourage users to take a specific action. A redesign\r\n     can include more prominent CTAs to encourage users to take the desired\r\n     actions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Updating Content&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Redesigning\r\na website can also provide an opportunity to update the content. This can\r\ninclude refreshing existing content, adding new content, or reorganizing the\r\ncontent to make it easier to find. Updating content can help businesses improve\r\ntheir SEO, provide more value to users, and establish themselves as an\r\nauthority in their industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improving brand identity&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A\r\nwebsite is often the first impression that a potential customer has of a\r\nbusiness. Redesigning a website can help businesses improve their brand\r\nidentity by creating a website that is consistent with their branding,\r\nmessaging, and overall marketing strategy. This can help build trust and credibility\r\nwith potential customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Streamlining Processes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Redesigning\r\na website can also help businesses streamline their processes. By analyzing the\r\nuser journey and identifying areas where users may encounter obstacles,\r\nbusinesses can create a website that is more efficient and easier to use. This\r\ncan save time and resources for businesses and improve the overall user\r\nexperience.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In\r\nconclusion, there are numerous benefits to redesigning a website. By improving\r\nthe user experience, enhancing mobile responsiveness, improving SEO, updating\r\ndesign trends, increasing conversion rates, updating content, improving brand\r\nidentity, and streamlining processes, businesses can create a website that is\r\nmore effective, efficient, and valuable for their customers. While redesigning\r\na website can be a significant investment, the potential benefits make it well\r\nworth considering.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improved Security&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot; mso-bidi-font-family:calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#252525;=&quot;&quot; mso-ansi-language:en-in;mso-fareast-language:en-in;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Website\r\nsecurity is more important than ever, especially with the increasing prevalence\r\nof cyberattacks. A website redesign can help to improve security by ensuring\r\nthat the website is built with security in mind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1679298378_benefits-of-website-redesign.png', 'benefits-of-a-website-redesign', '2023-03-20 07:46:18', '2023-03-20 08:29:35');
INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `bcatid`, `message_from`, `metadesc`, `metakeyword`, `message`, `file_path`, `slug`, `date_created`, `date_updated`) VALUES
(29, 11, 'Why Website Design is Essential for Small Businesses', 'website design is an important role for growing your business, read this article to know Why Website Design is Essential for Small Businesses.', 'website design, website development, website development company', '&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;In the modern virtual age, online presence for small companies is now not an alternative; this is a necessity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A well-designed website can be a recreation-changer, presenting a platform to reach a wider target market, establish credibility, and force growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In this article, we will dive deeper into exploring the essential function, advantages, satisfactory practices, and vital issues of website design for small organizations. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Virtual Age and Small Enterprise&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-left:3px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Digital Transformation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The virtual revolution has changed the way businesses operate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;From advertising and income to purchaser engagement and operations, nearly every aspect of running a small business has been touched by the digital age.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;This shift has given rise to new opportunities and challenges, making it imperative for small businesses to evolve and develop within the digital panorama.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Importance of Online Presence&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A strong online presence is the cornerstone of achievement in the latest enterprise global.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;This not handiest allows small organizations to reach a global audience but also promotes consideration and credibility among potential clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;The center of this online presence is an effective website, which serves as a digital storefront and the number one point of interaction among businesses and their audience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;1- Importance of website design&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Power of first impact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Inside the virtual sphere, your website regularly serves as the first point of contact among your enterprise and capacity clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Simply as the arrival of a bodily keep can affect a client&#039;s decision to go into, the design of your website plays a vital position in developing a high-quality first effect.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A properly designed internet site attracts site visitors, and builds self-assurance and curiosity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Navigability and user revel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Consumer experience (UX) is in the middle of website design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A well-established and user-pleasant internet site ensures that site visitors can easily discover the information they want, explore your offerings, and entire the preferred motion, which includes making a buy or contacting your business. .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;User-pleasant navigation will increase engagement and reduce leap rates.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Your internet site is an extension of your brand:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Powerful website design includes your emblem&#039;s colorations, fonts, brand, and messaging, growing a cohesive and remarkable revel for site visitors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;In an era dominated by smartphones and capsules, cellular responsiveness cannot be compromised.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A responsive internet site seamlessly adapts to distinctive display screen sizes and devices, making sure a regular and enjoyable user revels in for all visitors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Cellular friendliness additionally has an advantageous effect on seek engine rankings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Loading pace and overall performance Internet site speed matters greater than ever:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Users assume internet pages to load quickly and engines like Google take into account the loading pace while ranking websites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;An effectively designed internet site with optimized pix and code no longer most effectively keeps users engaged but also increases your visibility in seeking results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Search engine optimization (SEO)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Website design for small businesses and search engine optimization are interconnected.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;A properly based website with clean code, proper titles, and relevant content material makes it less difficult for serps to crawl and index your pages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Effective SEO practices, such as keyword optimization and exceptional one-way links, assist growth of your site&#039;s visibility in seeking consequences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;2- Advantages of website design for Small businesses:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stronger Reliability&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt; A professionally designed internet site affords consideration and credibility to ability customers. This indicates that your commercial enterprise is set up and committed to providing a first-class online experience. Conversely, a poorly designed or previous internet site can discourage capacity clients and damage your logo&#039;s popularity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Increased attain and Visibility&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt; The internet provides an international platform for small corporations to showcase their products and services. A well-designed website is to be had 24/7, allowing you to attain a wide target market irrespective of geographic boundaries. This increased attain can result in elevated income and logo popularity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Price-effective:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Advertising compared to standard advertising and marketing strategies which include print media or television, a website is a value-effective marketing device. It permits you to promote your commercial enterprise, percentage content material, and connect with clients without the recurring costs associated with offline advertising and marketing efforts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Uninterrupted client interplay: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Your website acts as a customer service consultant around the clock. It enables clients to find out about your offerings, ask questions, and make purchases at their convenience. Modern-day website design includes analytics equipment that provides valuable records about your site visitors&#039; conduct. You could tune metrics like web page perspectives, jump prices, and conversion fees to benefit insights into what works and what wishes improvement.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Those statistics-pushed insights tell your advertising and business strategies.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Competitive gain In an aggressive market&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;: &lt;/b&gt;A well-designed internet site can set you apart from opponents. It showcases your precise proposition cost and facilitates you stand out in the minds of ability clients. Your website may be a game-changer in a crowded market.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;3- High-quality Practices in website design&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Outline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Your dreams before diving into website design, it&#039;s vital to make clear your targets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What do you want to gain with your website?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Whether or not it&#039;s producing leads, selling products, or imparting statistics, the clean information of your dreams informs the design procedure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;User-centered design positioned your target audience first:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Understand your target market&#039;s wishes, possibilities, and pain points.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Tailor your website&#039;s design, content, and capability to cater on your target market, ensuring a person-centered revel in.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Simplicity and clarity :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Simplicity in layout often yields high-quality outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Keep your website smooth and uncluttered, that specializes in clear navigation and straightforward messaging.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Avoid overwhelming site visitors with immoderate visuals or complicated layouts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Cellular Optimization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Layout your internet site with mobile users in thoughts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;4- Website design structures and gear:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Content management structures (CMS)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Popular CMS platforms like WordPress, Joomla, and Drupal provide consumer-friendly interfaces for website creation and management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;They provide a wide range of themes and plugins to customize your web page&#039;s design and functionality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Web designers and builders can create a website that aligns perfectly with your logo and goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot; times=&quot;&quot; new=&quot;&quot; roman&quot;,serif&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;Consult us a Website Expert of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mkstechnosoft.com/website-development-in-patna.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Website Development company in Patna&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for all kinds of website design and development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1705481603_why-website-design-is-essential-for-small-businesses.jpg', 'why-website-design-is-essential-for-small-businesses', '2023-10-31 19:01:31', '2024-01-17 14:23:23'),
(30, 11, 'How to create a business website for free using google my business', 'How to create a business website for free using google my business', 'How to create a business website for free using google my business', '&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Introduction:&lt;/b&gt; In today&#039;s digital age, having an online presence is crucial for the success of any business. Fortunately, Google provides a powerful and free tool for creating a business site: Google My Business. This platform not only helps businesses manage their online presence but also allows them to build a simple yet effective website without any cost. In this step-by-step guide, we&#039;ll walk you through the process of creating a business site for free using Google My Business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Step-by-Step Guide: Creating a Business Site for Free with Google My Business&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 1:&lt;/b&gt; Sign in or create a Google account. If you don&#039;t already have a Google account, you&#039;ll need to create one. Once you&#039;re signed in, go to the Google My Business website (&lt;a style=&quot;&quot; target=&quot;_new&quot;&gt;https://www.google.com/business/&lt;/a&gt;) and click on &quot;Manage Now&quot; to get started.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 2:&lt;/b&gt; Enter your business information. Provide essential details about your business, such as the business name, category, and location. Make sure to verify your business location on the map accurately. This information is crucial for local search visibility.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 3:&lt;/b&gt; Access the Website Builder After completing the initial setup, navigate to the &quot;Website&quot; tab on the left sidebar of your Google My Business dashboard. Click on &quot;Create a Website&quot; to access the website builder.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 4:&lt;/b&gt; Choose a Template Google My Business offers a variety of templates tailored to different business categories. Select a template that aligns with your business type and reflects your brand identity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 5:&lt;/b&gt; Customize Your Website Once you&#039;ve chosen a template, you can start customizing your website. Add your business logo, choose a color scheme, and personalize the content to showcase your products or services. Google My Business simplifies the process with drag-and-drop functionality, making it easy for users with little to no web design experience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 6:&lt;/b&gt; Add Essential Business Information Ensure that your business site includes key information such as contact details, business hours, and a brief description of your products or services. This helps potential customers find and understand your business quickly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 7:&lt;/b&gt; Preview and Publish Before making your site live, take advantage of the preview feature to see how it looks on both desktop and mobile devices. Once you&#039;re satisfied with the appearance and content, hit the &quot;Publish&quot; button to make your business site accessible to the public.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step 8:&lt;/b&gt; Optimize for SEO. To improve your site&#039;s visibility in search engine results, optimize it for search engines. Add relevant keywords to your content, include high-quality images, and regularly update your business information.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Conclusion:&lt;/b&gt; Creating a business site for free using Google My Business is a straightforward process that can significantly enhance your online presence. By following these steps, you can establish a professional and user-friendly website that helps potential customers discover and connect with your business. Take advantage of the tools provided by Google My Business to stay competitive in the digital marketplace.&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/1705481307_how-to-create-a-free-website-on-google.jpg', 'how-to-create-a-business-website-for-free-using-google-my-business', '2024-01-17 14:11:16', '2024-01-17 14:18:27');

